# Network Module - VPC, Subnets, NAT Gateway, Security Groups
# To be implemented in Phase 3

# Resources to be created:
# - aws_vpc - Main VPC (10.0.0.0/16)
# - aws_subnet - Public subnets in us-east-1a and us-east-1b
# - aws_subnet - Private subnets in us-east-1a and us-east-1b
# - aws_internet_gateway - Internet gateway
# - aws_nat_gateway - NAT gateway in us-east-1a
